attributes.name: CAKE BATTER 3.5g
attributes.body: Descending from popular strain Wedding Cake, Cake Batter is more energetic than its parent. Connoisseurs appreciate its complex, vanilla frosting smell and fuel aftertaste. This strain is high in THC with an accelerated, euphoric onset that isn't for newbies. Just like cake batter itself, you might not want to indulge too much at a time.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Chemmy Jones
attributes.body: Meet Chemmy Jones, a Sativa strain born from the genetic fusion of Chem D and Casey Jones. Offering an invigorating and refreshing encounter with a high THC content, Chemmy Jones brings forth a functional, high-energy buzz that fosters productivity. According to customer reviews, this strain is celebrated for its ability to promote energy, upliftment, and happiness. Its aroma and taste showcase diesel undertones harmonized with a floral sweetness.

attributes.name: Ripple - Balanced
attributes.body: The golden ratio, for functional moments of bliss. Hybrid-like effect. 100mg THC + 100mg CBD per container. That is 10mg THC + 10mg CBD per powder packet.

attributes.name: Ripple - Revive
attributes.body: For self-care anywhere and necessary daily pauses. Hybrid-like effect. 100mg THC + 100mg CBG per container. That is 10mg THC + 10mg CBG per powder packet.

attributes.name: Ripple - Pure
attributes.body: Pure THC for a clear headed high. Sativa-like effect. 100mg THC per container. That is 10mg THC per powder packet.

attributes.name: Ripple - Sleep
attributes.body: Fall asleep fast. No melatonin, no sugar, no staring at the ceiling. Indica- like effect. 100mg THC + 50mg CBN per container. That is 10mg THC + 5mg CBN per powder packet.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

Black Mamba 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Black Mamba is an indica-dominant hybrid strain known for its dark, dense buds and potent effects. It often has a sweet and earthy aroma with hints of spice. Black Mamba delivers a strong, long-lasting high, inducing deep relaxation, sedation, and a dreamy, introspective state.

attributes.name: GMO 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: GMO, short for Garlic, Mushroom, and Onion, is an indica-dominant hybrid strain with a distinct and pungent aroma reminiscent of its name. It typically offers a combination of savory and earthy flavors. GMO is known for its potent effects, including deep relaxation, euphoria, and potential appetite stimulation.

attributes.name: White Fire OG 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: White Fire OG, also known as WiFi OG, is a hybrid strain that combines the genetics of Fire OG and The White. It generally has a pungent, diesel-like aroma with earthy undertones. White Fire OG provides a powerful and uplifting cerebral high along with deep relaxation and potential pain relief.

attributes.name: Apple Jacks 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Apple Jacks is a sativa strain that combines the genetics of Jack Herer and White Widow. It usually has a sweet and fruity aroma with hints of apple and citrus. Apple Jacks provides a stimulating and energetic high, promoting mental clarity, focus, and a sense of happiness.

attributes.name: Ghost Train Haze 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Ghost Train Haze is a potent sativa-dominant strain known for its high THC content. It often has a citrusy aroma with hints of floral and spice. Ghost Train Haze produces a strong cerebral high, characterized by intense euphoria, creativity, and an uplifting, energizing effect.

attributes.name: Slurricane 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Slurricane is a hybrid strain with a sweet and fruity profile. It typically offers a combination of flavors reminiscent of tropical fruits and berries. Slurricane is known for its potent effects, producing a deep physical relaxation and a calm, blissful state of mind.
